page.title: 16KENNELS, HIGH WYCOMBE
page.content:
The{kennels}are at Ragman's Castle. This is where they breed Cocker Spaniel dogs.They also board dogs belonging to people who have gone on holiday,leaving their animals behind.The dogs have won prizes at Crufts the all England dog show. The lady does all the work herself,feeding them and keeping them clean.She has fifty-three dogs.The lady there has made a stable and a barn into kennels for all the dogs. The{kennels}are made of wood.They are surrounded by barbed wire so that dogs can't get out
